CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 2, 1955, pg. 28 reads: "Free Prizes, Samples and Demonstrations Galore...4. Miss Willa Rogers charmed visitors from the Oswald and Hess booth by passing out delicious bits of O&H Wieners...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Willa Rogers standing in the Oswald and Hess Weiners booth in Syria Mosque for the 1955 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
